verses.text:
Lift him up, 'tis he that bids you, Lift the dy-ing, look and live;
Lift him up, the pre-cious Sav-ior, Bear the mes-sage God doth give;
Lift him up by liv-ing for him, Lift the Sav-ior up in prayer;
Lift him up by walk-ing with him, Show his love and ten-der care.

Lift him up, for sin has taint-ed All the hearts of men that live;
Lift him up by sin-ners need-ed, He a-lone can save for-give;
Lift him up, the pre-cious Sav-ior, Bear the mes-sage God doth give.
